### Jinja2 template (`jdbc_datastore.json.j2`)
This template creates the JSON payload for the datastore creation API call.

```json
{
  "name": "PostgreSQL Datastore",
  "type": "JDBC",
  "jdbcUrl": "jdbc:postgresql://{{ db_server_ip }}:5432/pingfed",
  "driverClass": "org.postgresql.Driver",
  "username": "{{ db_username }}",
  "password": "{{ db_password }}",
  "validateConnectionSql": "SELECT 1",
  "maskValuesInLogs": false
}
